extendedInfo.description: Get the latest news, advice and help if you are looking to move to Australia or New Zealand on your phone or tablet.Australia & New Zealand magazine is the ONLY magazine for anyone wanting to emigrate downunder. Every month you can read the facts about living in iconic cities like Sydney, Wellington or Melbourne, and get advice that will save you both time and money - from people who have already made the move. Plus get money off flights and tickets to Down Under Live, the Uk's leading emigration expo.
